title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - The Bullet Time
description:
This is new epic trailer, with 3D prerendered gun and bullet.
9 source placeholders: text/logo/footage.
As always it is very easy to use, just write your text or insert logo/image/fooatge 

in any source.
Trapcode Particular plugin is required.
There is 2 versions of project: with OpticalFlares and with prerendered OpticalFlares.
Sound FX included.
Video Tutorial is included.
